dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Fond du Lac County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2021 and includes the layers 'Fond_du_Lac_Hydro_LINE_2021' and 'Fond_du_Lac_Hydro_POLY_2021'.[Linear Features representing streams and artificial flow through water that are used to form a transport network. Water features such as Lakes, Reservoirs, Wide Streams and River, and Unspecified Open Water features.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download
